        div
          button[class="mx-auto flex justify-self-center py-3 px-6 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-escala-naranja hover:focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-escala-naranja" type="submit"]
            | Prueba Escala Ahora
      